<lb ed="I" n="0228a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>韓永義等造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan><cb:div>
<pb n="0229a" xml:id="I01.0085.0229a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229a01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0229a0101">邑主韓永義　維那魏元預　香火李英雄　邑子張子訓　邑子郭子逵
<lb ed="I" n="0229a02"/>邑主高元仁　維那魏紹□　香火孫子璨　邑子李阿察　邑子邊和穆
<lb ed="I" n="0229a03"/>齋主李伯□　典坐倪士康　邑老劉遵和　邑子田祖暉　邑子袁伏恩
<lb ed="I" n="0229a04"/>齋主□□寶　典坐趙仲略　邑老張和仁　邑子宋子暢　邑子劉士鸞
<lb ed="I" n="0229a05"/>中正霍羅侯　坐主鄧道隆　邑老栢延暉　邑子夏侯貴　邑子楊進國
<lb ed="I" n="0229a06"/>中正殷子琴　坐主翟多仁　邑子夏侯和　邑子范道仁</p></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0229b" xml:id="I01.0085.0229b" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0229b0101">迦<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">毗</unclear>羅神王
<lb ed="I" n="0229b02"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b03"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b04"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b05"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b06"/>像主王小貴供養
<lb ed="I" n="0229b07"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b08"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b09"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b10"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b11"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b12"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b13"/>像主夫人賀供養
<lb ed="I" n="0229b14"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b15"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b16"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b17"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b18"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229b19"/>那羅延神王</p></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0229c" xml:id="I01.0085.0229c" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229c01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0229c0101">妙<note n="0229001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB08073"/>＝旨【史】</note><note n="0229001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB08073"/>【佛拓】，旨【史】</note><app n="0229001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旨</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB08073"/></rdg></app>幽微。非聖無以盡於源。聖行之興。非
<lb ed="I" n="0229c02"/>福智莊嚴。豈能弘其道。然今合邑諸人等。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c03"/>宿殖<note n="0229002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">朙＝明【史】</note><note n="0229002" resp="ihp" type="mod">朙【佛拓】，明【史】</note><app n="0229002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">朙</rdg></app>珠。久歷諸佛。故能異心同<note n="0229003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31068"/>＝契【史】</note><note n="0229003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31068"/>【佛拓】，契【史】</note><app n="0229003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">契</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB31068"/></rdg></app>。仰慕
<lb ed="I" n="0229c04"/>遺蹤。在於定光像<note n="0229004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31069"/>＝前【史】</note><note n="0229004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31069"/>【佛拓】，前【史】</note><app n="0229004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">前</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB31069"/></rdg></app>。敬造七佛寶堪。并二
<lb ed="I" n="0229c05"/>菩薩。賢聖諸僧。<note n="0229005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB02793"/>＝彌【史】</note><note n="0229005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB02793"/>【佛拓】，彌【史】</note><app n="0229005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB02793"/></rdg></app><note n="0229006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31171"/>＝勒【史】</note><note n="0229006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31171"/>【佛拓】，勒【史】</note><app n="0229006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勒</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB31171"/></rdg></app>下生。梵王帝釋。舍利
<lb ed="I" n="0229c06"/>非<note n="0229007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31172"/>＝壹【史】</note><note n="0229007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31172"/>【佛拓】，壹【史】</note><app n="0229007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">壹</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB31172"/></rdg></app>。其<note n="0229008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30645"/>＝金【史】</note><note n="0229008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30645"/>【佛拓】，金【史】</note><app n="0229008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">金</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30645"/></rdg></app>容赫弈。照曜三千。<note n="0229009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31070"/>＝華【史】</note><note n="0229009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31070"/>【佛拓】，華【史】</note><app n="0229009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">華</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB31070"/></rdg></app>麗二相。妙
<lb ed="I" n="0229c07"/>菀八十。剋木圖<note n="0229010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">埿＝泥【史】</note><note n="0229010" resp="ihp" type="mod">埿【佛拓】，泥【史】</note><app n="0229010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">泥</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">埿</rdg></app>。像而非喻。採壁模形。焉
<lb ed="I" n="0229c08"/>是其譬。睹之者淨信開<app type="star" corresp="#0229002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">明</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">朙</rdg></app>。虔禮者三鄣殄
<lb ed="I" n="0229c09"/>息。斯乃塵勞之中。紹如來種。籍此勝<note n="0229011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB13224"/>＝善【史】</note><note n="0229011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB13224"/>【佛拓】，善【史】</note><app n="0229011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">善</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB13224"/></rdg></app>。仰
<lb ed="I" n="0229c10"/>願國祚永隆。三寶增盛。法界四生。七世先
<lb ed="I" n="0229c11"/>靈。存<note n="0229012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">兦＝亡【史】</note><note n="0229012" resp="ihp" type="mod">兦【佛拓】，亡【史】</note><app n="0229012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亡</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">兦</rdg></app>父母。現在眷屬。發菩提心。<app type="star" corresp="#0229005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB02793"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0229006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">勒</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB31171"/></rdg></app>下
<lb ed="I" n="0229c12"/>生。恒為導首。開化群迷。廣修万行。共集<app type="star" corresp="#0229011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">善</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB13224"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0229c13"/>根。同證菩提之道。刊銘頌曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c14"/>法性如如。非有非<note n="0229c1401" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【佛拓】【史】</note><app n="0229c1401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】 【史】">旡</rdg></app>。體非分別。妙用非虛。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c15"/>八相成道。似同凡夫。生而非生。滅而非滅。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c16"/>神通隱顯。摩王歸軼。化導三千。人天獨步。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c17"/>改迷接聖。慈悲覺<note n="0229013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB00322"/>＝寤【史】</note><note n="0229013" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB00322"/>【佛拓】，寤【史】</note><app n="0229013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寤</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB00322"/></rdg></app>。示三空門。令遊正路。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c18"/>淨修波若。四攝資助。奮翼道品。菩提永固。
<lb ed="I" n="0229c19"/>　　天統三年歲次丁亥三月壬申朔十五日丙戊建</p></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0229d" xml:id="I01.0085.0229d" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0229d01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0229d0101">比丘道最　　比丘法賢　洛州都兼治中奉朝請皇甫士通　洛陽郡中正姜範
<lb ed="I" n="0229d02"/>比丘曇暉　　比丘道標　征東將軍洛州大中正平恩縣開國男皇甫迥
<lb ed="I" n="0229d03"/>比丘洪猛　　比丘洪湛　冠軍將軍洛州金墉鎮前車騎府司馬趙思榮
<lb ed="I" n="0229d04"/>比丘慧蘭　　比丘道定　邑子趙遵明
<lb ed="I" n="0229d05"/>比丘法建　　比丘明海　邑子范敬賓
<lb ed="I" n="0229d06"/>景明寺法和　比丘曇樂　邑子樂季和</p></cb:div></cb:div>
